1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,280
The sound of my front door is distinct.

2
00:00:03,280 --> 00:00:07,520
You couldn't mistake it for any other sound in my house.

3
00:00:07,520 --> 00:00:12,440
The door, frame, and latch were all metal.

4
00:00:12,440 --> 00:00:20,440
It made an awful click, scrape, and slam every time you opened and then closed.
